  "steps": [
    {
      "title": "Vieta shortcut: sum of solutions $= -b/a$",
      "content": "For $32x^2 - (16a + 2b)x + ab = 0$, identify $A = 32$, $B = -(16a+2b)$.<br/>$$\\text{sum} = -\\frac{B}{A} = \\frac{16a+2b}{32}$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Factor and match to $k(8a+b)$",
      "content": "$$\\frac{16a+2b}{32} = \\frac{2(8a+b)}{32} = \\frac{8a+b}{16} = \\frac{1}{16}(8a+b)$$<br/>So $k = \\dfrac{1}{16}$. Therefore the value of $k$ is <strong>1/16</strong>."
    }
  ]
}